<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 18 Feb 2022 12:38:46 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Sony A1 以 1/32,000 秒快門拍攝子彈　立陶宛攝影師：需跟隨運動員射擊節奏</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/18/sony-a1-1-32000/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-a1-1-32000</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 18 Feb 2022 10:38:58 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086909</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>2022 北京冬季奧林匹克運動會正進行得如火如荼，有攝影師在冬季兩項（Biathlon）比賽進行其間利用 Sony [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>2022 北京冬季奧林匹克運動會正進行得如火如荼，有攝影師在冬季兩項（Biathlon）比賽進行其間利用 Sony A1 模仿 Nikon Z9 進行攝影，同樣捕捉到子彈離開步槍的畫面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.27.28.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.27.28-694x490.png" alt="" width="694" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.27.28-694x490.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.27.28-768x542.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.27.28.png 992w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/dranginisvee/">Vytautas Dranginis Facebook</a>)</p><p>日前，瑞典運動攝影師 Göran Strand 曾利用 Nikon Z9 於正在德國拍攝由越野滑雪與射擊項目結合的冬季兩項（Biathlon）賽事。而立陶宛攝影師 Vytautas Dranginis 效法 Göran Strand，利用 Sony A1 在冬季兩項比賽的射擊部分中，同樣拍攝到了 6 張清晰的子彈發射照片。</p><p>Dranginis 表示，作為一位運動攝影師，有必要擁有一部能準確的對焦和高速連拍的相機。因此，使用電子快門的 Sony A1 每秒能做出 30 張高速連拍、每秒 120 次自動對焦運算是非常有用的功能。</p><p>起初在拍攝時，他在白天以 1/2,000 秒的快門速度拍攝，但只能拍到一團輕煙。後來改用 1/6,400 秒快門，雖然可以見到子彈的身影，但仍然不通拍下子彈停下來的畫面，後來他再把快門速度提升 1/32,000 秒才能捕捉到子彈。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.23.51-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.23.51-1-694x509.png" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.23.51-1-694x509.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.23.51-1-768x564.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.23.51-1.png 1038w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.10.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.10-694x530.png" alt="" width="694" height="530" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.10-694x530.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.10-768x587.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.10.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.00.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.00-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.00-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.00-768x512.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-18-16.21.00.png 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/dranginisvee/">Vytautas Dranginis Facebook</a>)</p><p>Dranginis 又指，以短間隔方式拍攝，跟隨運動員的射擊節奏，可節省記憶卡空間，「你需要比子彈稍微快一點，但要有耐性，最好還有足够的記憶卡。」。他分享自己會聆聽第一發槍聲，在第二發子彈射出前才按下快門為目標，在第二發槍聲響起才鬆開快門掣，重複以上步驟再拍攝下一張相片。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://petapixel.com/2022/02/16/olympic-photographer-catches-bullets-in-mid-air-with-the-sony-alpha-1/">petapixel</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=3kH34hAPWug:7Dh_zLjnN-E:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=3kH34hAPWug:7Dh_zLjnN-E:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】threezero HulkBuster　最強可動性＋可擺爆地 Pose</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/18/threezero-hulkbuster-mk44/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=threezero-hulkbuster-mk44</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Chris]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 18 Feb 2022 10:21:02 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[玩具]]></category><category><![CDATA[Hulkbuster]]></category><category><![CDATA[Iron Man]]></category><category><![CDATA[marvel]]></category><category><![CDATA[Threezero]]></category><category><![CDATA[threezero HulkBuster MK44]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086569</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Iron Man 大家都耳熟能詳，亦已經推出過不少相關產品，但今日要和大家開箱評測的是 threezero 最 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Iron Man 大家都耳熟能詳，亦已經推出過不少相關產品，但今日要和大家開箱評測的是 threezero 最新推出的 DLX HulkBuster 浩克毀滅者 Mark 44，而並非常見的 Iron Man 設計。而這隻 DLX HulkBuster Mark 44 共有 65 處可動，可動性似乎相當高，事不宜遲，就讓我們一起看看這隻 HulkBuster 的厲害之處吧！</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086572 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06956-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06956-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06956-807x900.jpg 807w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06956-768x857.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06956.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086587 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06963-475x580.jpg" alt="" width="475" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06963-475x580.jpg 475w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06963-738x900.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06963-768x937.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06963.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" /></p><h2><strong>開窗式包裝 「大隻」還原度高</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今次 HulkBuster 的外包裝盒採用開窗式磁鐵吸附設計，其實與以往的設計風格差不多，可見作品還原度頗高。而打開後便能看到圖片介紹以及主體，今次的 HulkBuster 高約 30cm，看起來非常「大隻」，而 1:12 的比例造型還原度相對高，頗有心思之作。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086573 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06979-557x580.jpg" alt="" width="557" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06979-557x580.jpg 557w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06979-865x900.jpg 865w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06979-768x799.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06979.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 557px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ HulkBuster 高約 30cm，看起來相當「大隻」</span></p><h2><strong>塗裝上色細節工整美觀</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">再看配件部份，手型方面則備有兩款造型，分別是發砲手和正常的放鬆手型，非常一目了然。而且塗裝質感相當不錯，漆面的上色非常工整美觀，採用了紅金銀配色，金屬質感非常強。</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">整體造型上亦做了許多的細節處理，外型很銳利，稜角分明，看起來頗為整齊簡潔。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086588 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06965-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06965-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06965-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06965.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 整體塗裝上色工整美觀，但未有作舊化處理</span></p><h2><strong>三個發光位燈光柔和，操作簡單但燈光較暗</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而今次 HulkBuster 總共有三個發光燈位，分別位於頭部，胸部和背部的推進器，開啟方式亦都非常簡單，臉部版件底下有一個小撥片，只需用手輕輕向前撥便可以開啟頭燈，而胸燈亦只需按下中間的反應堆便可開啟。今次 HulkBuster 的燈光做了磨砂霧面處理，整體燈光看起來非常柔和，而掀開後背的金色部分便會發現燈的開關，只要按下開關，在其身上的 6 個位置便會著燈，但要注意的是燈光比較暗，並非電池電量不足引致，而是原本的燈光便較為暗。不過美中不足的是小腿的燈位看似可以亮起，但其實只是裝飾，令小編空歡喜一場。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086574 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06994-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06994-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06994-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06994.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 背部的推進器燈位，但燈光可見較暗</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086580 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07008-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07008-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07008-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07008.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 胸前的亮燈位</span></p><h2><strong>整體可動性出色，手臂可靈活移動</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而 HulkBuster 其中一個賣點便是出色的可動性，小編實測這隻 HulkBuster 的頭部版件可以左右轉動及抬頭，而肩甲的地方亦設有一個雙重可動關節，只要在活動時先將肩甲移到旁邊便可以靈活移動手部板件，外面的位置亦同樣可以活動，手臂轉動也沒有問題。另外其備有一個往外拉伸的關節，可提高其他關節的可動度，內裡亦設有細節刻畫，算是相當有心思。另外上臂位置亦可轉動，平舉時裡面亦會跟住轉動。加上其本身的關節可以平抬超過 90 度，除了關節有點緊之外基本沒有其他問題。手臂的位置有一個彈簧關節，做彎曲動作的時候會自動進行避讓，彎曲超過 90 度都不在話下。另外手臂上的電擊槍也有一定的活動幅度，只要將外甲拔出來再向上推，就可以打開裡面的砲管進行拉伸動作，整體把玩起來非常靈活順手。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086575 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06972-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06972-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06972-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06972.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 頭部以及手臂關節靈活</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086581 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06992-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06992-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06992-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06992.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 手臂抬起後可見內裡亦設有細節刻畫，算是相當有心思</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086592 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06990-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06990-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06990-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06990.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 手臂平舉可</span>超過 90 度，裡面亦會跟住轉動</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086593 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06981-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06981-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06981-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06981.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 手臂備有彈簧關節，做彎曲動作時會自動進行避讓</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086582 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06986-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06986-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06986-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06986.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 手臂上的電擊槍是可變形的</span></p><h2><strong>腰部可動驚人，防穿崩設計不錯</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今次 HulkBuster 的手腕是一個頗大的球形關節，活動範圍非常不錯，但手腕沒有可動性，替換</span>手型時有點難操作。而胸部的側擺幅度頗大，左右活動都完全沒有問題。而腰部的可動更是相當厲害，前後彎腰的幅度非常大，而且防穿崩設計十分不錯，絕對是這個作品的一大亮點。而裙甲位置則是採用球形關節結構，與以往 threezero 的設計風格有些許不同，而整個關節軸心設在背面位置，把玩的時候可以利用球形關節對應不同的方向調整，使得動作更加靈活。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086589 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06988-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06988-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06988-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06988.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086576 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07001-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07001.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 腰部可動相當驚人，可向前彎近 90 度</span></p><h2><strong>腿部可動優秀，小心關節之間易碰撞</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而腿部位置設有一個下拉關節和內設了一個齒輪下拉關節，兩個下拉關節同時使用時前踢幅度可輕鬆達至 90 度，即使是單腳站立時側踢亦非常輕鬆。而膝部關節和大腿及小腿後的裝甲之間亦有連動設計，彎曲時可動性非常優秀，而腳的部分有一個拉伸關節用以左右接地，活動幅度非常大，即使腳尖以及後腳跟等的裝甲亦可自由活動。但把玩時需小心留意關節之間容易發生碰撞，因此操作上需要更加小心。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086577 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07014-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07014-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07014-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07014.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 腿部可動性出色，膝部關節和大腿及小腿後的裝甲設有連動設計</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086590 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07005.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 腳掌及腳後跟等裝甲亦可自由活動</span></p><h2><strong>駕駛艙可打開還原電影造型　關節緊實用力需小心</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">另一大賣點便是可以在駕駛艙中裝入半身的 Iron Man Mark 43，還原電影中由 Iron Man 親自駕駛的場景造型。而開啟的過程亦非常簡單，首先要取下卡扣，並將肩膀位置移到旁邊，避免在打開的時候刮蹭到肩膀位置。之後再將腋下關節位拉出來，但要留意因為軸心位置並不太受力，而且關節位置比較緊實，因此頗難拔出，需小心處理不要弄斷。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1086591" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06997-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06997-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06997-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06997.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 駕駛艙可裝入半身的 Iron Man Mark 43</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086578 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06977-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06977-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06977-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06977.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 駕駛艙可打開還原電影造型，可放下半身的 Iron Man Mark 43</span></p><h2><strong>整體過程頗輕鬆，展開後零件不易鬆脫</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而將兩邊胸前的裝甲拔出後，便可將肩膀上的裝甲拔出，而肩膀裝甲內裡則採用雙重金屬可動關節，相對較為緊實一點，不怕鬆脫問題。而再將胸前位置向兩邊打開，並記得將頸部後方的一塊小裝甲扣起向下拉，便可以避免頭部向上揭起時造成的磨擦。小編認為整體打開裝甲的過程算是頗為輕鬆，即使新手亦能上手。而且展開後各部分的零件亦並不易鬆脫，雖然在一定程度上概括地簡化了一些細節，但整體來說尚算不錯，既不複雜亦能同時表達相應效果，而且打開後內層亦有加入不少細節刻畫。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086579 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07003-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN07003.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 但打開關節較為緊實，因此過程需較小心</span></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086583 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06964-510x580.jpg" alt="" width="510" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06964-510x580.jpg 510w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06964-791x900.jpg 791w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06964-768x873.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06964.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 510px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086586 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06958-634x580.jpg" alt="" width="634" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06958-634x580.jpg 634w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06958-983x900.jpg 983w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06958-768x703.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06958.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 634px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 由於可動性高，更可擺出最靚的爆地 Pose</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086585 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06975-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06975-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06975-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06975.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>總結：綜合素質出色，可動性出色+亮燈功能</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今次這款 HulkBuster 綜合各方面的造工以及質素均是非常出色的作品，造型還原度高的同時亦能做到亮燈開甲功能以及一流的可動性，關節緊實度和細節亦做得相當不錯，小編認為非常值得入手。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086584 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06967-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06967-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06967-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/KAN06967.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
